{
  "stem": "4760.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Naturally, he was a spoiled brat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he-- he went to school in France, but I didn't have the chance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were-- I was in school in Germany until '38.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After the-- After I finished school, eighth grade, my parents finally decided to send us because it was so bad in Germany-- children couldn't go out, we couldn't do this, we couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my parents finally sent both my sister and I to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had a bar mitzvah when I was 13.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was my father who taught me the whole bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knew a  lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he-- he even taught my children their bar mitzvahs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] So I have to say, I have good memory of my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he came from--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came from the town of [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Simon. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Simon ?] was a bigger town, and they had acquired a big Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he came only twice a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he had to teach there, and he had to teach there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, and you know, in those days, the people didn't have anymore not that much money, either, anymore, because of Hitler, they weren't allowed to do the business like they used to.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had two separate rooms where the teacher would teach us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even have a picture of all the children who were [LAUGHS] in-- in Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home, at home, at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did that at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when it came to read the Torah, then naturally we would go to the synagogue and open up the Torah, and would learn-- read out of the Torah in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Leave to France, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was the most joyable day because, you know, we knew now we're going to become free.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
